                        <interp inst="t18450818-name-904" type="given" value="HENRY JOHN"></interp>HENRY JOHN RATCLIFF</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a surgeon. I saw the prosecutor—he was insensible, and had a compound concussion of the brain.</p>
